;W[fe]C[The invasion at C12 and this are the prequisites of an ancient opening called the "Big Corner Pattern." Wang Hannian and Zhou Donghou used to employ it. In the basic opening C10 is not present, but here it gives Black's shape great flexibility. Therefore in the end Wang wisely abandoned this opening.]
